1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:08,500
This world is rotten.

2
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:14,000
Criminals keep increasing, and justice is powerless.

3
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:22,000
What is this? "Death Note"... a notebook of death?

4
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:29,500
"The human whose name is written in this note shall die."

5
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:36,000
Ridiculous. It must be someone's prank.

6
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:44,500
But... what if it were real?

7
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:52,000
"The writer must have the subject's face in mind when writing the name, or it will not take effect."

8
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,500
In other words, people with the same name won't die by mistake.

9
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:07,000
"If the cause of death is not specified, the subject will die of a heart attack."

10
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:14,500
A heart attack... meaning it would appear to be a natural death.

11
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:22,000
"When writing the details of death, it must be done within six minutes and forty seconds."

12
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:29,000
Should I test it... No, there's no way someone would actually die.

13
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:37,500
However, if this notebook is real,
I can change the world.

14
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:45,000
I will judge criminals and create a new world.

15
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:52,500
I will... carry out justice with this notebook.

16
00:01:56,000 --> 00:02:00,000
No one will be able to stop me.

17
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:08,500
I will become the god of the new world.

18
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:16,000
Using this Death Note,
I will build the ideal world.
